author: Obhie Salvador
text:
‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è A Truly Exceptional Anytime Fitness Branch ‚Äì Siglap CC

I just have to say ‚Äì this is hands down the best Anytime Fitness branch I‚Äôve ever been to! The moment you step inside, you‚Äôre greeted not just by a clean, well-organized space, but also by the warmest, most welcoming team of staff I‚Äôve ever met.

A special shoutout to Ms. Candy, Putri, Noraini, and Mr. Shamil ‚Äì each of you makes this gym feel like a second home. Your friendliness, approachability, and genuine care for members go far beyond expectations. It‚Äôs rare to find staff who not only greet you with a smile but also actively engage and build relationships with everyone who walks through the door.

What sets this branch apart isn‚Äôt just the people (though they are incredible!) ‚Äì it‚Äôs the overall environment. The place is spotlessly clean, well-organized, and smells fresh ‚Äì a big contrast to other gyms that often feel stuffy or cluttered.

One of my favorite things here is the thoughtful little touches the team adds ‚Äì like the adorable mini pantry stocked with bread and a variety of spreads, and the regular member engagement activities. Whether it's themed events, wellness activities, or casual catch-ups, they always find a way to keep members involved and appreciated.

To the amazing team of four: thank you so much for your hard work, positivity, and dedication. Your efforts don‚Äôt go unnoticed ‚Äì you‚Äôve created not just a gym, but a true community. This is by far the best place to stay fit, healthy, and happy!

text: I‚Äôve been a regular member at this gym for over a year now, and it‚Äôs been a fantastic experience! The facilities are always clean and well-maintained, and the atmosphere is motivating. author: Dee Dee Colleur
text: Love love this gym. However, the instructor is really quite incorrigible. He uses the gym as a user and interrupts a paying user. Instructor wanted to use a single cable pull down but a paying female customer was in his way, so he asked her if he could use it. Prior to that, I saw him using the double cable. He placed the sitting bench in front of said cable machine. After usage, he did NOT move the seated bench but just proceeded to use another station. That is truly selfish. It must be noted that this centre has notices plastered around the gym, instructing users to return the weights, even threatening a $20 fine. And here we have their own instructor, refusing to replace the seated bench back to it's original place. That seated bench has no wheels and for some ladies and the elderly, it can be a problem.

text:
Just joined this gym, culture here is great generally w ppl wiping down as they go. The only HUGE issue I hv here is the heavy metal blasting on the speakers as soon as you enter the gym. You can hear the screaming through yr earbuds. Only staff has access to the audio so I‚Äôm writing in to ask the mgmt, for the sake of all that is holy, pls either turn the audio off or pls put something palatable like the radio on.

Update: The noise seems to hv improved, but the jury is still out..

I'm taking this opp to commend Lucas for his professionalism and his energy; he is a real credit to his organisation. Always polite and considerate, he does not hesitate to help anyone who needs it, and this plays a big part in making the gym a place for everyone, both gym rats and newbies!

author: Tak
text:
I had a very disappointing experience with Lucas, the ex-manager at this gym. His behavior was rude, and he was consistently unreliable, which made my time at the gym uncomfortable and frustrating.

I understand that Lucas has moved on to manage at another gym, but I feel the owner should be wary and consider mentoring him. There is definitely room for improvement in his professionalism and attitude. Without proper guidance, he could bring similar issues to his new role, affecting the experience for others.

I hope the owner takes this feedback seriously and helps Lucas develop into a more reliable and respectful manager.

author: Imran Saleh
text:
I've never previously awarded a business such a low rating, but I am now awarding Anytime Fitness Siglap CC a well-earned single star, and here's why:

I had scheduled an appointment at the gym to update the credit card details on my account. The representative with whom I interacted via the gym's WhatsApp channel confirmed a 12:30 pm appointment. However, when I arrived at the said time, the counter was unmanned. After waiting for 15 minutes, I approached an in-house trainer and explained my situation. He asserted that he hadn't been informed of my appointment and made it clear that this matter wasn't his responsibility. He offered to contact the manager, and I found myself waiting another 30 minutes. Eventually, another staff member arrived, whom I assumed to be the manager. She, too, professed ignorance about my appointment, explaining that the staff member who had been coordinating with me did not inform them.

To the franchise owner, if you happen to read this, I must express my disappointment. This is not an acceptable way to operate a business. I am leaving my rating at one star until you can explain why it's okay to leave a paying customer waiting for 45 minutes, continuously shift responsibility, and offer no apology whatsoever.
